-- clikae Ghostty launcher template. One placeholder (the LAUNCH_CMD token on the
-- do-shell-script line below) is substituted by lib/commands/app.sh with a
-- fully-built, shell-quoted `open -na Ghostty.app --args ...` command.
--
-- Ghostty's macOS CLI can't open a terminal window directly (`ghostty` only runs
-- "+actions" on macOS), so we go through `open -na Ghostty.app --args`, passing
-- the window title via --title= and the profile command via -e. The placeholder
-- has the @ delimiters that this comment omits, so substitution never touches
-- this text.

on run
    do shell script "@LAUNCH_CMD@"
end run
